    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and it's been smoke-free and pet-free. It drives like a dream and is sparkling clean inside and out. You won't find another one this clean! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
