    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, an exemplary specimen of high-revving, naturally aspirated engineering. This unit features the coveted F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC powerplant, delivering linear power through a crisp, short-throw 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains factory-stiff with its signature X-bone frame, supported by a precision-tuned double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen helical limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. Meticulously maintained with an unblemished finish and a pristine interior, this vehicle retains its original VIN tags on all panels. No mechanical modifications; strictly OEM components. A turn-key investment for the discerning collector seeking the pinnacle of analog driver engagement.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
