    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner and kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with professional ceramic coating and zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirls. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having followed a rigorous break-in procedure and receiving scheduled maintenance exclusively at authorized dealerships. Every button, feature, and electronic system functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. All original keys, manuals, and service records are included.",
